[0.000, "o", "\u001b[K\u001b[8d; register constants casesensitive\u001b[K\u001b[9;19Hcom.autoregister-casesensitive\r\u001b[10d;com.autoregister_casesensitive = false\u001b[12;3Hshow warnings on duplicate constant registrations\u001b[K\u001b[13;3Hhttps://php.net/com.autoregister-verbose\u001b[K\r\u001b[14d;com.autoregister_verbose = true\r\u001b[15d\u001b[K\u001b[16d; The default character set code-page to use when passing strings to and from COM objects.\r\u001b[17d; Default: system ANSI code page\r\u001b[18d;com.code_page=\u001b[K\r\u001b[19d\u001b[K\u001b[20d; The version of the .NET framework to use. The value of the setting are the first three parts\r\u001b[21d; of the framework's version number, separated by dots, and prefixed with \"v\", e.g. \"v4.0.30319\".\r\u001b[22d;com.dotnet_version=\u001b[K\r\u001b[23d\u001b[K\u001b[24d[\u001b[30m\u001b[43mmbstring\u001b[39;49m\u001b[m\u000f]\u001b[K\r\u001b[25d; language for internal character representation.\r\u001b[26d; This affects mb_send_mail() and mbstring.detect_order.\u001b[27;3Hhttps://php.net/mbstring.language\u001b[K\r\u001b[28d;mbstring.language = Japanese\u001b[K\r\u001b[29d\u001b[K\u001b[30d; Use of this INI entry is deprecated, use global internal_encoding instead.\r\u001b[31d; internal/script encoding.\u001b[32;3HSome encoding cannot work as internal encoding. (e.g. SJIS, BIG5, ISO-2022-*)\u001b[K\u001b[33;4Hf empty, default_charset or internal_encoding or iconv.internal_encoding is used.\u001b[34;3HThe precedence is: default_charset < internal_encoding < iconv.internal_encoding\r\u001b[35d;mbstring.internal_encoding =\r\u001b[36d\u001b[K\u001b[37d; Use of this INI entry is deprecated, use global input_encoding instead.\r\u001b[38d; http input encoding.\u001b[K\r\u001b[39d; mbstring.encoding_translation = On is needed to use this setting.\u001b[40;3HIf empty, default_charset or input_encoding or mbstring.input is used.\u001b[K\u001b[41;3HThe precedence is: default_charset < input_encoding < mbstring.http_input\u001b[42;3H"]
